<headline>Heat Advisory issued June 20 at 2:51AM CDT until June 20 at 8:00PM CDT by NWS Amarillo</headline>
<description>...HEAT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 1 PM THIS AFTERNOON TO 8 PM CDT THIS
EVENING...
* WHAT...Hot temperatures up to 105 degrees expected.
* WHERE...Palo Duro Canyon State Park.
* WHEN...From 1 PM this afternoon to 8 PM CDT this evening.
* IMPACTS...Hot temperatures may cause heat illnesses.</description>
<instruction>Take extra precautions when outside. Drink plenty of fluids. Wear
lightweight and loose fitting clothing. Try to limit strenuous
activities to early morning or evening. Take action when you see
symptoms of heat exhaustion and heat stroke.</instruction>
